{
  "stem": "3874.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were 50 of us on the transport, on this children's transport.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We all stuck our heads out of the window.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, the parents were waiving goodbye as the train left.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the last thing I remember is my father sort of jogging after the train on the platform.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he always wore a pen and pencil set in his suit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And his-- his pen and pencil set fell out of his jacket pocket.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He bent down to pick it up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then the train curved-- it curved around the corner.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was the last time I saw them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The idea was that they were going to follow me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had no reason to-- I mean, I had been away from my parents before.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For instance, in '36 or '37, they'd sent me and my brother to Italy for the whole summer on a vacation, to a children's camp.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was a very pleasant experience.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, I recognize, this was very different-- but I was very sure that they were going to follow me at some point in time.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Maybe three months, four months, they'll pick me up and we'll start life someplace else.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, I did not recognize at the time that, even if they had come and picked me up and started a life someplace else, my life would have been very, very different than it had been as a middle class youngster growing up in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I knew my way around Vienna, for instance, very well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I took street cars, and I used to go all over the place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, at 10 years old, I knew Vienna like inside out.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
